import Mathlib
open TopologicalSpace Metric Set Filter Asymptotics Function MeasureTheory AffineMap Bornology
open scoped Topology Filter NNReal Real

/-- If U ‚äÜ ‚ÑÇ is open and f : U ‚Üí ‚ÑÇ is holomorphic and injective, then f'(z) ‚â† 0 for every z ‚àà U. -/
theorem injective_holomorphic_nonvanishing_derivative {U : Set ‚ÑÇ} (hU : IsOpen U) {f : ‚ÑÇ ‚Üí ‚ÑÇ}
    (hf : DifferentiableOn ‚ÑÇ f U) (hf_inj : Injective f) :
    ‚àÄ z ‚àà U, deriv f z ‚â† 0 := by sorry
